<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact - Open Bankruptcy Project</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Contact the Open Bankruptcy Project for press inquiries, research collaboration, or general questions.">
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://openbankruptcyproject.org/contact.html">
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">

    <meta property="og:title" content="Contact - Open Bankruptcy Project">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Press inquiries, research collaboration, and general questions.">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://openbankruptcyproject.org/contact.html">

    <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-053Z64N82F"></script>
    <script>
        window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
        function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}
        gtag('js', new Date());
        gtag('config', 'G-053Z64N82F');
    </script>

    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        :root {
            --bg: #0d1117;
            --surface: #151b23;
            --border: #252d38;
            --text: #e6edf3;
            --text-secondary: #b1bac4;
            --text-muted: #7d8590;
            --accent: #58a6ff;
            --accent-hover: #79b8ff;
        }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.7;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }
        a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
        a:hover { color: var(--accent-hover); }
        .container { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px; }

        nav {
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 18px 0; position: sticky; top: 0;
            background: rgba(13,17,23,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); z-index: 100;
        }
        nav .nav-inner { max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; }
        .nav-brand { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); }
        .nav-brand a { color: var(--text); }
        .nav-brand a:hover { text-decoration: none; }
        .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .nav-links a { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 500; }
        .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }

        .page-header { padding: 72px 0 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
        .page-header h1 { font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .page-header .subtitle { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }

        .content { padding: 56px 0; }
        .content p { color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; }

        .contact-grid {
            display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px; margin-top: 32px;
        }
        .contact-card {
            background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 28px;
        }
        .contact-card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .contact-card p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 12px; line-height: 1.7; }
        .contact-card .email {
            display: inline-block; font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--accent); word-break: break-all;
        }

        .note-block {
            background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 28px; margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .note-block h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .note-block p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; margin: 0; }

        footer {
            padding: 48px 0 40px; text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.82rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        footer .footer-links { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        footer .footer-links a { color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0 12px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; }
        footer .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
        footer p { margin-bottom: 6px; line-height: 1.6; }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container { padding: 0 20px; }
            .page-header { padding: 48px 0 32px; }
            .page-header h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            .content { padding: 40px 0; }
            .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
    <div class="nav-inner">
        <span class="nav-brand"><a href="/">Open Bankruptcy Project</a></span>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="about.html">About</a>
            <a href="research.html">Research</a>
            <a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Contact</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">We welcome inquiries from researchers, journalists, legal aid organizations, and the public.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="contact-grid">
            <div class="contact-card">
                <h3>General Inquiries</h3>
                <p>Questions about the project, our tools, or our mission.</p>
                <a class="email" href="mailto:info@openbankruptcyproject.org">info@openbankruptcyproject.org</a>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-card">
                <h3>Press &amp; Media</h3>
                <p>Interview requests, story inquiries, and press materials.</p>
                <a class="email" href="mailto:info@openbankruptcyproject.org">info@openbankruptcyproject.org</a>
            </div>
            <div class="contact-card">
                <h3>Research Collaboration</h3>
                <p>Academic partnerships, data sharing, and methodology review.</p>
                <a class="email" href="mailto:info@openbankruptcyproject.org">info@openbankruptcyproject.org</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="note-block">
            <h3>Important Note</h3>
            <p>The Open Bankruptcy Project does not provide legal advice. We cannot assist with individual bankruptcy cases, recommend attorneys, or interpret how the law applies to your specific situation. If you need legal assistance, please contact a licensed attorney in your jurisdiction or your local legal aid office.</p>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

<footer>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="footer-links">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="about.html">About</a>
            <a href="research.html">Research</a>
            <a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/ilikemath9999" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
        </div>
        <p>Open Bankruptcy Project is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization.</p>
        <p>EIN available upon request. All tools and data released under open source licenses.</p>
    </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
